GOOGLE_API_KEY="<you-api-key-here>"
OPENAI_API_KEY="<you-api-key-here>"
SILICONFLOW_API_KEY="<you-api-key-here>"

## Database
### S3 (Bucket storage)
AWS_ACCESS_KEY_ID="<you-access-key-id-here>"
AWS_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY="<you-secret-access-key-here>"

### Postgres (Relational Database)
SUPABASE_URL="https://<project-ref>.supabase.co"
DATABASE_URL="postgresql://postgres:<your_password_here>@localhost:5432/postgres"
# Supabase Storage (chat file uploads)
#    Found in Supabase dashboard > Project Settings > API
SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY="<your-service-role-key-here>"
SUPABASE_STORAGE_BUCKET="chat-uploads"

### Redis (In-memory Database)
# Local: redis://:<password>@localhost:6379
# Upstash (TLS): rediss://default:<password>@<endpoint>.upstash.io:6379
REDIS_URL="redis://:<your_redis_password>@localhost:6379"

# Upstash REST API (optional, used for serverless / HTTP transport)
# Found in Upstash console > Database > REST API
UPSTASH_REDIS_REST_URL="https://<endpoint>.upstash.io"
UPSTASH_REDIS_REST_TOKEN="<your_upstash_rest_token>"

### Qdrant (Vector Database)
# Local: http://localhost:6333
# Qdrant Cloud: https://<cluster-id>.<region>.cloud.qdrant.io:6333
QDRANT_URL="http://localhost:6333"
# Required for Qdrant Cloud, leave blank for unauthenticated local instances
QDRANT_API_KEY=""

## APIs
### url: https://www.n2yo.com/login/edit/
### content: fetch satellites data in real-time
N2YO_API_KEY="<you-api-key-here>"

### url: https://app.tavily.com/home
### content: search data on the web
TAVILY_API_KEY="<you-api-key-here>"
